{
    "id": "noiseboy",
    "name": "NOISEBOY",
    "version": "0.7.0",
    "abbrev": "NOIZB",
    "description": "Chromatically-pitched noise + filter / Karplus-Strong instrument. Velocity brightness moved to a separate post-mix OUTPUT FILT so it no longer detunes notes. Lighter bitcrush. db-cell always runs on the output, gated silent between notes.",
